 together?   In other words, if you say have +5 rp and +7 item, will your bonus be +12, or +11 at level 50? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usunthasbayne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sunthas Bayne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/11/02 3:33:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1670.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bonus cap</span><hr size=1> Good question.<br>
<br>
Any proof that Realm Point bonuses are working outside of envenom? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uditherdaoc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dither DAoC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/11/02 4:42:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1670.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.boomspeed.com/dither/smiley2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bonus cap</span><hr size=1> If you reequip yourself, realm rewards are counted before your items are, so 1 point of items wont show up.  For instance, my friend is a rank 2 hunter, level 38.  his cap is +8.  he is wearing +9 in stealth items, but only +7 are showing up in the actual number.  This is due to 1 of the +9 being over his cap, and his realm reward counting as another +1. <p>Dither Disgustipated<BR>
Kobold Shadowblade<BR>
Ragnarok, Palomides</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usunthasbayne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sunthas Bayne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/11/02 5:18:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1670.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bonus cap</span><hr size=1> At 41 the Maximum Bonus from Items/Realm Ranks is 9 correct?<br>
<br>
So if I go home and max out my Parry skill I have 3 items (well 4 if you include gloves in the bank) Cloak has +2 Parry, Bracer has +3 Parry, Sword has +4 Parry. (Gloves have +3 Parry).<br>
<br>
I am Realm Rank 2, Level 2. I should have +1 to all stats (Invisible ofcourse.)<br>
<br>
Base Parry is 27, your saying I should see Parry hit 35 (+1 for invisble parry). <br>
<br>
If it hits 36 then either Realm Rank rewards are broken or they stack with items.<br>
<br>
correct? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvalarauco.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Valarauco</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/11/02 5:25:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1670.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~bdemong/valaface.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bonus cap</span><hr size=1> &quot;If it hits 36 then either Realm Rank rewards are broken or they stack with items. correct? &quot;<br>
<br>
Yes, though I believe Dither just stated that this won't happen; it will cap at 35. <p><img src="http://home.attbi.com/~bdemong/valarauco.gif"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uditherdaoc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dither DAoC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/11/02 7:14:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1670.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.boomspeed.com/dither/smiley2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bonus cap</span><hr size=1> Aye, make sure to take everything off first though.  If I remember correctly, If you hit your realm rank while maxxed on items, your number won't go down until you reequip the items. <p>Dither Disgustipated<BR>
Kobold Shadowblade<BR>
Ragnarok, Palomides</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usunthasbayne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sunthas Bayne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/11/02 8:08:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1670.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.webpak.net/~njb/emblemsm.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bonus cap</span><hr size=1> Ok guys, what am I doing wrong here?<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.webpak.net/~njb/images/32parry.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
This was my starting parry.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.webpak.net/~njb/images/36parry.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
Then I equiped my Parry+4 Sword. Should have put me at 35 according to the above info.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.webpak.net/~njb/images/27parry.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
Just to make sure, I took off all my items and put them on again.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.webpak.net/~njb/images/realmrank.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
Realm Rank 2, Level 2, Level 41. <br>
<br>
Something not adding up here. <p>"Tanks with AE Nukes! WOOT!"
