strength=3>
<font size=1 color=#000000 face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>
 Sunthas Bayne<BR>Firbolg Hero<br>Guild Leader - Dei Gratia</table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=majin>Majin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/11/02 8:21:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1670.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bonus cap</span><hr size=1> To summarize above info :<br>
<br>
You are lvl41, your max benefit from items is (41/5)+1 = ~ 9<br>
<br>
Your base parry is 27 , thus you are able to get to 36.<br>
<br>
You are able to get to 36 only  with items, your invisibil +1 parry point doesnt add here.<br>
<br>
So, through the pics , its 100% proof that they dont add together (would be insane anyway, why would anyone need +skill items anymore ?)<br>
<br>
Good figure <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uditherdaoc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dither DAoC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/11/02 10:09:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1670.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.boomspeed.com/dither/smiley2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bonus cap</span><hr size=1> His pic could be showing 3 things.  Realm rewards aren't kicking in, Realm rewards are seperate from items in terms of the cap, or realm rewards are factored in after his items are.<br>
<br>
I wonder if it matters when you hit realm rank as to when the realm points are figured in.Unfortunately, envenom is the only real test to see how this works out, but it is very unlikely to find a rogue with enough +envenom items to hit his cap, that also is realm rank 2. <p>Dither Disgustipated<BR>
Kobold Shadowblade<BR>
Ragnarok, Palomides</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukosmaul.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kosmaul</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/12/02 1:07:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1670.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.home.net/gevry12/daoc/emblem WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bonus cap</span><hr size=1> im getting close to R2, but cant help w/ your test. only found items so far w/ +env give you max +5<br>
