</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=javelin>Javelin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/6/02 4:13:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1670.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> test</span><hr size=1> Couldn't you test it with +Crit items, just splat a grey to see if the cap has gone up? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=ebullition>Ebullition</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/6/02 4:20:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1670.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: test</span><hr size=1> I logged weapon skill before I hit Realm Rank 3.  When I hit Realm Rank 3 my weapon skill did increase.  <br>
<br>
So I have both Envenom and Weapon Skill data that verifies that Realm Rank bonuses work<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usunthasbayne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sunthas Bayne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/6/02 4:23:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1670.topic&index=12>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: test</span><hr size=1> This seems like its too hard to test. I have another 30k rps to get for realm rank 3, so when I get close I will start doing some tests. <br>
<br>
I suppose I could do a test now if I could find another Hero with Large Weapon Skill at or close to their level (as we can use a couple items to help balance it) and then use the same weapon to wack a mob. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uraginok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raginok</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/8/02 12:04:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1670.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: test</span><hr size=1> Sun, I have been under the impression that Realm Rank bonus only affects your skills in RvR action, not PvM.  I have yet to meet a member of the enemy realm who will stand still and let you and another hero of similar skill and level take turns beating him so you can compile test results to form an analysis here.  If you find such a person, would you please allow me to take part in this test simply for fun? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
